imdb.plot outline: Follow five teens named Hannah, Sarah, Mike, Emily, and Matt as they love, laugh, cry, and betray their way through the fictitious school year. They all know one another and each has a secret. These include secret loves, cheating in class, and even that one of them burned down their school. These secrets will be revealed to you as they don't know that their private video diaries have been hacked and uploaded for the world to see.
imdb.title: Hacked Diaries: School Fire
plot: Five students are having their private video diaries hacked and one video is being uploaded daily.

Follow five teens named Hannah, Sarah, Mike, Emily, and Matt as they love, laugh, cry, and betray their way through the fictitious school year. They all know one another and each has a secret. These include secret loves, cheating in class, and even that one of them burned down their school. These secrets will be revealed to you as they don't know that their private video diaries have been hacked and uploaded for the world to see.
